</h4>
<ul class="reset smalltext" id="msg_717340_extra_info">
<li class="title">骰神牧师<li class="postgroup">Chivary<li class="stars"><img src="Themes/celeste/images/pip.gif" alt="*" border="0"/><img src="Themes/celeste/images/pip.gif" alt="*" border="0"/><img src="Themes/celeste/images/pip.gif" alt="*" border="0"/><img src="Themes/celeste/images/pip.gif" alt="*" border="0"/><img src="Themes/celeste/images/pip.gif" alt="*" border="0"/><li class="avatar" style="overflow: auto;">
