<h5 id="subject_717342">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=608b062285b07a8dd1e4c54d0838ba14&amp;topic=75920.msg717342#msg717342" rel="nofollow">Re: 【译文】Sword World RPG Adventure 2 信天翁号追击！</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_717342'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_717342'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #4 于:</strong> 2015-04-21, 周二 04:50:14 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_717342_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
